50|$|The Seychelles Hindu Kovil Sangam {{was founded}} in 1984. The annual Kavadi festival is a major event which is a {{government}} holiday for all Hindus. Cultural troupes are invited {{from time to time}} to enhance cultural values and links. The organization of the Seychelles <b>Hindu</b> <b>Council,</b> celebration of Deepavali festival on a national scale and the setting up of a crematorium with government support are events worthy of note. There is also a <b>Hindu</b> <b>Council</b> of Seychelles established and maintained by the community.|$|R
